Images in Bootstrap 
-------------------

<img src="..." class="img-fluid" alt="Responsive image">    



Image thumbnails
-----------------

<img src="..." alt="..." class="img-thumbnail">


Aligning Images
----------------

1. <img src="..." class="rounded float-left" alt="...">

2. <img src="..." class="rounded float-right" alt="...">

3. <img src="..." class="rounded mx-auto d-block" alt="...">

4. <div class="text-center">
   <img src="..." class="rounded" alt="...">
   </div>
